All the basic functionalities implemented. 
To run the dragon 
./ray -w 512 -r 1 -d 17 -a 1 scenes/polymesh/dragon.ray out1.bmp
I have two strategies you can change it by a flag. d and l are depth and leafe max min 

You can change the rest of the things using UI. like anti aliasing and smooth shading
